Breaking News App:
- Views latest top-highlight news.


- Users can register and login to post new news and comments.


-  Show the latest news with different categories like entertainment, finance, education, stocks, international news, covid data, etc. 



- Shows a weather icon in the navbar, we can click and view current weather data in different cities, 
and also can search and add weather of the selected city.


- Api  for news: - https://newsapi.org/v2/top-headlines?country=us&apiKey={API KEY}


- Api for weather: - http://api.openweathermap.org/data/2.5/forecast?id=524901&appid={API key}


-Api for covid-data:- https://covid-19-statistics.p.rapidapi.com
